tetris-deepin (0.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Migrate to Qt6/DTK6.
  * Generate 8-bit music and sound effects programmatically.
  * Add raccoon logo to about dialog.
  * Start music on game start.
  * Add missing translations: LEVEL, LINES, Pause, Resume.
  * Update GitHub Actions for Qt6/DTK6 (Ubuntu 24.04 + Deepin crimson repo).
  * Update debian packaging for Qt6/DTK6.

